{"tid":569613,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"《心理繪圖投射法》你畫我答 （新）","createTime":"2018-02-23T00:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T18:32:37.000Z","uid":112205,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d245d80e42197c1e428081209c8b1a0c901dc95f","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T00:49:05.000Z","msg":"上一個post 夜晚急住打做得唔好<br />\n所以今早再重新出發<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遊戲玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 首先準備一張A4白紙<br />\n<br />\n2. 先用一分鐘沉思心中的畫面<br />\n<br />\n3. 畫中必須包括四項元素： 屋、樹、人、蛇<br />\n<br />\n4. 畫人不可以畫火柴人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n<br />\n5. 另外，請用三個形容詞形容蛇的心情/處境<br />\n<br />\n5. 畫好後，將相send 去我TG ，我會分析比你聽<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/ming12345678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fming12345678&d=46fcM0%2BWrLG%2F%2F9vNxla2UJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0b22f5ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/ming12345678</a><br />\n<br />\n#唔洗介意畫得靚唔靚<br />\n#有唔準的地方唔好介意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/084315_d82dda4f5271310409a784077006edef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F084315_d82dda4f5271310409a784077006edef.png&h=ace92a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依位巴打話我講得幾好，唔係巴納姆效應<br />\n在得到他同意下，up上黎做分享<br />\n.........................................................<br />\n「爸打 你為人較為內向內儉，傾向先觀察別人再展向心房，別人平常也難了解你，你自我防衛機制重，很多時候亦怕別人誤會你的想法<br />\n<br />\n童年過去有創傷（樹洞）<br />\n生活有煩惱落悶，有可能係關朋友事（落葉）<br />\n你不是那種太social able 的人，不會到處識人，社交圈子固定而集中，朋友對你來較比靠值得依靠<br />\n<br />\n個性方面，自信稍欠，唔係太清楚自己的為人、潛力、個性，情感上也較少發洩，但優點是願意踏實用雙手付出<br />\n<br />\n暫時未有甚麼夢想目標<br />\n<br />\n家是對你最安全的地方」<br />\n.......................................................<br />\n<br />\n暫時反應良好，大家快d賜我墨寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果大家覺得我ok既，請正評和同意我分享圖畫"},{"pid":"ee4e94abe6ffe624cf8596eb48385b839811610b","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/090257_656f887c3ce16bfafb7455e601e8e56c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F090257_656f887c3ce16bfafb7455e601e8e56c.png&h=a2c04f73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一位巴打<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/090358_ce1ffbcf25d63f024f4229cc4668b62b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F090358_ce1ffbcf25d63f024f4229cc4668b62b.png&h=8b3d95b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中左有脾氣，但巴打話佢會發出黎<br />\n但朋友位，佢覺得有d差異，唔係我講得咁好"},{"pid":"1a224eeaf327377faeea3fe5eaf37f07f933ce00","tid":569613,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:15:31.000Z","msg":"朝早無乜人上連登嫁"},{"pid":"47e60a68d90213ec3872fa2d1a8478837ad198bb","tid":569613,"uid":90034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:22:29.000Z","msg":"留個名今晩玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c134876799a26107e8478af3feabefa50a687b58","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T02:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/105258_98e19b8195f94175f6334c38e09d8a81.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F105258_98e19b8195f94175f6334c38e09d8a81.png&h=efa2bf05&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 相信努力付出會有成果<br />\n2. 童年過去有創傷或陰影<br />\n3. 絲打係有脾氣的人<br />\n4. 願意與人溝通 被人了解<br />\n5. 做事不馬虎，企理<br />\n6. 社交圈子單一及集中<br />\n7. 個性樂觀，但不是自信滿滿的人<br />\n<br />\n7中6，得5號point 唔中"},{"pid":"06680155325a571bc6613a32ffe0a1b9e6ad2f61","tid":569613,"uid":3951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"冇tg直接放上黎得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b776de285d7d6e31e619a9ece7f8f144bc35ecd","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06680155325a571bc6613a32ffe0a1b9e6ad2f61","tid":569613,"uid":3951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"冇tg直接放上黎得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"可以"},{"pid":"ad5af63c31c4f0d2aee30d4fe5459c477179dbfa","tid":569613,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/173016_c11bbdebc0e7a4ccf6351b9f90c3bdf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F173016_c11bbdebc0e7a4ccf6351b9f90c3bdf7.png&h=301c7cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蛇：美麗、自由、無害"},{"pid":"4042003aafd3d5863dd37de5d077657cb797786a","tid":569613,"uid":90860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T10:57:39.000Z","msg":"用小畫家畫得唔得"},{"pid":"a1bc1ce56f2af6de4ed21ab0a157946390ff2f70","tid":569613,"uid":31567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/203320_3a9bb5ed8369959fd86368ba699b9abf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F203320_3a9bb5ed8369959fd86368ba699b9abf.png&h=7570937c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蛇: 放鬆，靜默，張望<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打"},{"pid":"4bb120a331e2b57e077e2a9fa52e1ddd651facb5","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1bc1ce56f2af6de4ed21ab0a157946390ff2f70","tid":569613,"uid":31567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/203320_3a9bb5ed8369959fd86368ba699b9abf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F203320_3a9bb5ed8369959fd86368ba699b9abf.png&h=7570937c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蛇: 放鬆，靜默，張望<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"唔係香港，要明天覆"},{"pid":"7d295ea4755c2b3e36482e8e0079377a0e9e552f","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad5af63c31c4f0d2aee30d4fe5459c477179dbfa","tid":569613,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/173016_c11bbdebc0e7a4ccf6351b9f90c3bdf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F173016_c11bbdebc0e7a4ccf6351b9f90c3bdf7.png&h=301c7cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蛇：美麗、自由、無害"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:18:19.000Z","msg":"首先，我應該係集中睇屋 樹 人<br />\n但係巴打 依幅畫的精隨 係一條蛇到<br />\n所以不妨從條蛇先開始<br />\n<br />\n蛇好多時候都意味既係性，你仲要畫咁大條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以係巴打生活中，你覺得性對你黎講係好重要，而且係「美麗、自由、無害」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二，依幅圖帶有傳統中國風，你的屋寬而大 ，為人都大量不小器，而且自信滿滿。但間屋既似牌坊又似房屋，屋黎講就差點，別人唔知點了解你，冇窗冇門，所以可以講你都唔係好想人知你內心<br />\n<br />\n第三，人方面成個哪叱仔。公仔代表既係自我、代表既係個性，遇上咁大條蛇，佢一d都唔驚 咁淡定，巴打應該都係好獨立自在的人，但我唔覺得你個人係開心。<br />\n<br />\n第四 樹，易同人起衝突，關係糾紛多。"},{"pid":"d6787bbc749f220971ac570d95d6c91717c19802","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4bb120a331e2b57e077e2a9fa52e1ddd651facb5","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1bc1ce56f2af6de4ed21ab0a157946390ff2f70","tid":569613,"uid":31567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/203320_3a9bb5ed8369959fd86368ba699b9abf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F203320_3a9bb5ed8369959fd86368ba699b9abf.png&h=7570937c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蛇: 放鬆，靜默，張望<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"唔係香港，要明天覆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:22:20.000Z","msg":"1. 近朋友，遠離家人<br />\n2. 唔知自己個性 感受迷網<br />\n3. 過去興父母家庭關係一般 甚至有焦慮<br />\n4. 有d孤寂"},{"pid":"c7af65d69c7c78ed5542b15084d7bfafa45ec6d9","tid":569613,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:24:08.000Z","msg":"聽過屋樹人，未聽過屋樹人蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacac52d09dc43f19ecd3e7e558c0484158c35f4","tid":569613,"uid":65612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:25:27.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a23669a286618720da0a3084ee05258d5204cc89","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:27:48.000Z","msg":"一位絲打分享<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/082409_b4dcf8a25a8722db2e55661f9ecb67b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F082409_b4dcf8a25a8722db2e55661f9ecb67b1.png&h=c46cd4da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我的回應：<br />\n1. 人際關係唔係咁好<br />\n2.寂寞，欠溫暖<br />\n3. 冇人明白你<br />\n4. 你亦都唔比人去了解你<br />\n5. 你唔直接面對自己的感受<br />\n6. 你會回憶輕嘆<br />\n<br />\n絲打回應：<br />\n我本身有asperger 同adhd 所以生活上唔覺特別孤單 <br />\n雖然係獨行俠"},{"pid":"8c475f3254b114b2c40570e0503d67bfe88a4f46","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:30:39.000Z","msg":"另一位絲打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/082858_9373eafede72a167dd6a0e333ee73731.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F082858_9373eafede72a167dd6a0e333ee73731.png&h=0bb7943b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我的回應<br />\n1. 人際關係幾好 不同圈子都識到人<br />\n2. 相信努力付出係有成果<br />\n3. 有兩個家庭？（估錯）<br />\n4.有窗把 門鎖<br />\n絲打 係個細心注重細節的人<br />\n5.樂於被人認識溝通<br />\n6. 思維與常人不同 不願接受框架局限 喜歡走自己認為對的路<br />\n7. 自信<br />\n<br />\n絲打：除3之外都中"},{"pid":"b40ec18e9537b4ecd525a18751a9c9eb3d68051d","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7af65d69c7c78ed5542b15084d7bfafa45ec6d9","tid":569613,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:24:08.000Z","msg":"聽過屋樹人，未聽過屋樹人蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:31:19.000Z","msg":"要唔要玩下🐍 TG我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb58e6050549f50b0569a2196cff1d2b6733dff","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:33:35.000Z","msg":"各位爸絲唔好趙完我就鬆，比返個正評我先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377df3e81cc247373b4d4b944df1701f84c2adba","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4042003aafd3d5863dd37de5d077657cb797786a","tid":569613,"uid":90860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T10:57:39.000Z","msg":"用小畫家畫得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:34:27.000Z","msg":"唔好"},{"pid":"7159160086eef7501fc10f9df8ee64d87973633a","tid":569613,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b40ec18e9537b4ecd525a18751a9c9eb3d68051d","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7af65d69c7c78ed5542b15084d7bfafa45ec6d9","tid":569613,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:24:08.000Z","msg":"聽過屋樹人，未聽過屋樹人蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:31:19.000Z","msg":"要唔要玩下🐍 TG我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:17:35.000Z","msg":"唔得閒畫，用說話描述。<br />\n<br />\n線條散亂嘅素描畫。<br />\n<br />\n屋：<br />\n喺幅畫右方。破爛嘅鐵皮小屋，得一道長方木門，一對正方形窗。<br />\n<br />\n樹：<br />\n喺幅畫左方。一棵好似冬天咁枯乾咗嘅樹，樹枝唔多，葉得一兩塊黐喺樹枝末段。<br />\n<br />\n人：<br />\n喺棵樹右邊。個人係一個面目無情低頭嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n蛇：<br />\n喺棵樹地下躝梗，三角形頭，有殺氣，有想食咗個人嘅衝動。<br />\n<br />\n利申：亞氏保加抑鬱撚"},{"pid":"9237d5d56ecbdb29f3a46beefd9721830cabbfee","tid":569613,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:33:53.000Z","msg":"睇左reply先畫係咪會唔準?"},{"pid":"140d767a823791c86a9c30b4581c55d342a55fd6","tid":569613,"uid":31567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6787bbc749f220971ac570d95d6c91717c19802","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4bb120a331e2b57e077e2a9fa52e1ddd651facb5","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1bc1ce56f2af6de4ed21ab0a157946390ff2f70","tid":569613,"uid":31567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/203320_3a9bb5ed8369959fd86368ba699b9abf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F203320_3a9bb5ed8369959fd86368ba699b9abf.png&h=7570937c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蛇: 放鬆，靜默，張望<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"唔係香港，要明天覆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:22:20.000Z","msg":"1. 近朋友，遠離家人<br />\n2. 唔知自己個性 感受迷網<br />\n3. 過去興父母家庭關係一般 甚至有焦慮<br />\n4. 有d孤寂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:34:29.000Z","msg":"幾中"},{"pid":"a9e8b06163afa7e821e1fc6129c09a5e2953c270","tid":569613,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d295ea4755c2b3e36482e8e0079377a0e9e552f","tid":569613,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad5af63c31c4f0d2aee30d4fe5459c477179dbfa","tid":569613,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/173016_c11bbdebc0e7a4ccf6351b9f90c3bdf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F173016_c11bbdebc0e7a4ccf6351b9f90c3bdf7.png&h=301c7cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蛇：美麗、自由、無害"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T00:18:19.000Z","msg":"首先，我應該係集中睇屋 樹 人<br />\n但係巴打 依幅畫的精隨 係一條蛇到<br />\n所以不妨從條蛇先開始<br />\n<br />\n蛇好多時候都意味既係性，你仲要畫咁大條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以係巴打生活中，你覺得性對你黎講係好重要，而且係「美麗、自由、無害」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二，依幅圖帶有傳統中國風，你的屋寬而大 ，為人都大量不小器，而且自信滿滿。但間屋既似牌坊又似房屋，屋黎講就差點，別人唔知點了解你，冇窗冇門，所以可以講你都唔係好想人知你內心<br />\n<br />\n第三，人方面成個哪叱仔。公仔代表既係自我、代表既係個性，遇上咁大條蛇，佢一d都唔驚 咁淡定，巴打應該都係好獨立自在的人，但我唔覺得你個人係開心。<br />\n<br />\n第四 樹，易同人起衝突，關係糾紛多。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:54:08.000Z","msg":"4唔中 其他唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceefc1a9e4fa3e2b3a232864c0cbb1fb55531e9c","tid":569613,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T02:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/100931_182712ea5bc52d1b3daa19af5a0673d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F100931_182712ea5bc52d1b3daa19af5a0673d8.png&h=95312153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}